          "process_md": "> **Samagra ID Creation:**\n\n\n1. Visit the [official website](https://samagra.gov.in/default.aspx) and click on the &quot;[Register family](https://samagra.gov.in/Citizen/Pages/AddNewFamilyRegistration.aspx)&quot;.1. On the new page, enter the Mobile number which was linked with Aadhaar Number and authenticate via OTP.\n1. Now provide the Aadhaar number and enter the new OTP.\n1. On the new page, provide the basic details, complete address\n1. Give the consent and submit.\n\n<br>\n\n> **Apply Process:**\n\n\n1. Visit the official [Sambal Portal.](https://sambal.mp.gov.in/)1. Under &quot;Sevaaye&quot;, click on &quot;[Panchikaran Hetu Aavedan Kren](https://sambal.mp.gov.in/Public/Survey/ShramikRegApplicationeKYC.aspx)&quot;.1. Enter &quot;Samagra ID&quot; and &quot;Pariwar ID&quot;.\n1. Fill out the online application form with required details.\n1. Give the consent and submit.\n\n"
        }
